---
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-visual">
      <div class="avatar-wrap">
        <div class="avatar-bg"></div>
        <div class="avatar-initials">IA</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-num">195<span class="stat-plus">+</span></span>
          <span class="stat-label">Posts in 2017</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-num">2015</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Blogging since</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-num">3</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Content pillars</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
      <h2 class="about-heading">A storyteller at heart,<br /><em>a mother by grace.</em></h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        Hi there! I'm Iman, a beauty and parenting content creator based in Malaysia.
        This little corner of the internet is where I share everything I genuinely love —
        from the skincare routines that transformed my skin, to the honest, unfiltered
        journey through pregnancy and new motherhood.
      </p>
      <p class="about-text">
        Whether you're searching for a reliable sunscreen recommendation, tips on reducing
        acne scars, or simply want to feel less alone during the beautiful chaos of raising
        a little one — you can find it all here.
      </p>
      <div class="about-tags">
        <span class="tag">Skincare</span>
        <span class="tag">Makeup</span>
        <span class="tag">Pregnancy</span>
        <span class="tag">New Motherhood</span>
        <span class="tag">Baby Care</span>
        <span class="tag">Lifestyle</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Visual / Avatar side */
  .about-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .avatar-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 220px;
    height: 220px;
  }

  .avatar-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 60% 40% 55% 45% / 50% 55% 45% 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blush), var(--petal));
    animation: morph 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes morph {
    0%, 100% { border-radius: 60% 40% 55% 45% / 50% 55% 45% 50%; }
    33% { border-radius: 45% 55% 40% 60% / 55% 45% 60% 40%; }
    66% { border-radius: 55% 45% 60% 40% / 40% 60% 45% 55%; }
  }

  .avatar-initials {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .about-stat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: rgba(254, 240, 243, 0.5);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 213, 218, 0.4);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.2rem 0.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--rose-gold);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-plus {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--rose-gold);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Content side */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rose-gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--rose-gold);
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .about-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    background: rgba(254, 240, 243, 0.5);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 213, 218, 0.4);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .tag:hover {
    background: var(--blush);
    border-color: var(--blush);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-visual {
      order: -1;
    }

    .avatar-wrap {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
    }

    .avatar-initials {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
